2. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |    3    |    4    |     5     |    6    |     7     |
| Flower   | iris | amaryllis | balloon-flower | poppy | bellflower | sunflower | daffodil |

