.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, singing, skydiving, woodworking, sudoku, fishing, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3  |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | baking | cooking | fishing | woodworking | sudoku | singing | skydiving |

