.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: basketball, skateboarding, parkour, swimming, golf, rugby, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |   3    |    4    |     5      |   6    |  7  |
| Sport   | basketball | skateboarding | golf | handball | swimming | parkour | rugby |

 